      "checkId": "catch_without_rethrow"
    },
    "evidence": { "requireSnippet": true, "maxSnippetLines": 12 },
    "suggestion": "明确异常策略：记录关键上下文并 rethrow，或转换为业务异常/错误码并停止后续流程。"
